<h2>Enrollment Forms</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @application.parent_first_name %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for your enrollment fee payment! <%= @application.child_first_name %>'s spot in <%= @program.name %> is now secured.</p>

<p>To complete the enrollment process, please review and sign the following forms:</p>

<h3>Required Forms</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Family Agreement & Waiver</strong> - Our policies and liability waiver</li>
  <li><strong>Parent/Guardian Contact Form</strong> - Emergency contacts and pickup authorization</li>
  <li><strong>Medication Administration Form</strong> - If your child requires any medication</li>
  <li><strong>Health & Medical Care Form</strong> - Medical history and care preferences</li>
</ul>

<p>Please complete and return these forms by responding to this email or bringing them to your first day.</p>

<% enrollment_plan = @enrollment&.enrollment_payment_plan %>
<% if enrollment_plan %>
<h3>Payment Plan Selected</h3>
<p>
  <strong><%= enrollment_plan.payment_plan.name %></strong><br>
  Total Tuition: $<%= number_with_precision(enrollment_plan.total_amount, precision: 2) %><br>
  Enrollment Fee: $<%= number_with_precision(enrollment_plan.enrollment_fee, precision: 2) %> (paid)<br>
  <%= enrollment_plan.payment_plan.installment_count %> tuition payment(s) of $<%= number_with_precision(enrollment_plan.total_amount / enrollment_plan.payment_plan.installment_count, precision: 2) %>
</p>
<% end %>

<h3>What's Next?</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Complete and return the enrollment forms</li>
  <li>We'll confirm your enrollment once forms are received</li>
  <li>Your first tuition installment will be due according to your payment plan</li>
  <li>Mark your calendar for the first day of <%= @program.name %>!</li>
</ol>

<p>If you have any questions about the forms or the program, please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>

<p>We're so excited to welcome <%= @application.child_first_name %> to our nature-based learning community!</p>

<p>Warmly,<br>
The Nature Preschool Team</p>
